body.description: Degree Men Cool Rush Antiperspirant Deodorant delivers 48-hour sweat and odor protection to keep you feeling dry and fresh. This antiperspirant deodorant for men works as hard as you do and offers 48-hour protection, so you can take on the day. Our Cool Rush Antiperspirant Deodorant features a refreshing kick of crisp, arctic freshness. The powerful antiperspirant deodorant responds when you need it most, so you can stay confident without having to worry about slowing down. You can be confident you’ll be protected from sweat and odor by this antiperspirant for men. Stay fresh and feel clean from morning to night. Simply twist, glide and get moving. The crisp, energizing scent helps to keep you as fresh as when you started your day. Stay dry, cool, and confident thanks to Degree Men Cool Rush Antiperspirant Deodorant. At Degree, we want to inspire the confidence in everyone to move more and go further. We’re here to support your journey through an antiperspirant that moves with you and helps you go beyond your limits. As well as increasing our use of reusable materials, we’re making it easier for you to recycle our antiperspirant and dry spray packaging. Degree. It won’t let you down.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value and worth the money!
reviews.reviewText: Degree deodorant has always work very well for me! The Shower clean has been a staple in my house for the last 5 years or more. The shower clean scent is a very versatile it is suitable for male and female, which works for the entire family. I have used Degree for many years it is effective and will hold you ALL day and Night! With Degree deodorant you will not go wrong!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It leaves white residue on clothes, otherwise it's good
reviews.reviewText: I got this deodorant because I've read that it doesn't leave white stains on the armpits of shirts. However, this was wrong -- it DOES leave white residue. However I'm sticking with it for now. It has a good scent, fresh and clean smelling. It keeps my armpits dry. I love that it lasts 48 hours. And I love that it's in bulk because I know that I won't be needing to buy more deodorant for a while.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Switched to Degree after using Old Spice for a very long time, and I'm really pleased with it!It is hands-down the most effective deodorant and anti-perspirant I have tried in its price range. It manages my sweat and maintains a fresh scent throughout the day. 48-hours is an overly bold claim, I think, but this has easily lasted me a full day without needing to re-apply.The scent is pleasant, albeit a generic 'fresh' one. While I think Old Spice has it beat in the range and strength in the scent department, Degree flat out destroys it when it comes to longevity and effectiveness. The value for money with Degree is also a huge win.I can't see myself going back to another brand now. Congratulations, Degree, you've won me over!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My go-to deodorant/antiperspirant...
reviews.reviewText: No residue and very effective. Has a light, fresh scent. Usually at a great price, too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Best value out there. Great, clean scent and good protection. Workhorse product.
reviews.reviewText: I've purchased this multi-pack for years now and think it's a great value. I was long-loyal to Secret deodorant, but found it was drying and made my skin itch. There are no issues with that with Degree and it is a clean, invisible solid that doesn't make marks on my clothing. Each one lasts a long time and I'm not stinky or sweaty. Winning all around.Left a star off because they use a lot of chemicals to accomplish this. Would be a real winner if it could do all this and was also aluminum free or talc free.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I use this deodorant personally and like it. It smells good all day and lasts long. It's better than the gel deodorants that I've used for a long time. The gel gets all slimy, this deodorant goes on well and smells great. I got 2 of these 2 packs, because I gather supplies to give to the homeless and people in need in my community. This was a decent price for the 2 pack and it's a really good amount, it's a large stick of deodorant.
